    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/fd9a4f9969f3affaf0d1b2b65a30d137.poster.avif?t=1735015785\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/fd9a4f9969f3affaf0d1b2b65a30d137.webm?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/fd9a4f9969f3affaf0d1b2b65a30d137.mp4?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在单间地牢中扮演一位的小地牢管理员！这款游戏融合了Roguelike团队建设和策略性库存管理。你的小单间地牢就是你的堡垒，你必须巧妙地安排的仆从、奇幻的神器和有趣的物品，抵御那些调皮的冒险者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/dc5c11bcf08f10e8ae23437ad8f54747.poster.avif?t=1735015785\" width=320 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/dc5c11bcf08f10e8ae23437ad8f54747.webm?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/dc5c11bcf08f10e8ae23437ad8f54747.mp4?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特点:<br><br>基于网格的库存管理: 使用网格系统精确地组织你的地牢。每个物品都有其位置，成功取决于井井有条的安排。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/0ee29427795863a9270718ec4237c22d.poster.avif?t=1735015785\" width=720 height=772 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/0ee29427795863a9270718ec4237c22d.webm?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/0ee29427795863a9270718ec4237c22d.mp4?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>位置协同: 明智地安排你的单位和物品，激发强大的协同效应。合适的位置能决定胜负。<br>升级单位和物品: 随时间增强你的仆从和神器，使它们在对抗冒险者时更强大、更有效。<br>可旋转的物品: 旋转物品，使其完美地适应你有限的空间。每一格都很重要。<br>挑战性BOSS: 面对强大的BOSS，考验你的策略和地牢防御能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/878d2a9a292d6d083ed1f7bf3e5b760a.poster.avif?t=1735015785\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/878d2a9a292d6d083ed1f7bf3e5b760a.webm?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/878d2a9a292d6d083ed1f7bf3e5b760a.mp4?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>独特的初始角色和构建: 从各种初始角色中选择，每个角色都有独特的能力和游戏风格。试验不同的构建，找到最有效的策略。<br>在单间地牢中保护你的地牢，智胜冒险者，证明你是终极地牢管理员！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/6ce21a460a7d69d401f54ea60d12b6aa.poster.avif?t=1735015785\" width=500 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/6ce21a460a7d69d401f54ea60d12b6aa.webm?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065840/extras/6ce21a460a7d69d401f54ea60d12b6aa.mp4?t=1735015785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
